name: Limited Edition Pop 'stache Tee
description:
This shirt is the first in a series of limited edition t-shirts designed by some of our favorite designers. " " is brought to you by Becky Murphy from Waco, TX. There were less than 100 of these shirts printed on Tultex 0241 Heather Red tees.

To celebrate the launch of Pop 'stache, we're doing several runs of limited edition t-shirts. The first of which comes to you from Becky Murphy all the way down in Waco, TX. Grab 'em now while supplies last.
